{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/administrator/v1/deployment/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Portal Docs"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"909053fe-f2a0-5a7c-89bc-e995f4071a7d","html":"<h1>Deployments</h1>\n<p>There are two ways that Kudoo supports you releasing new versions of your app. Automated and manual.</p>\n<h2>Automated deployments</h2>\n<p>To get started using automated deployments there is some setup you’ll need to perform.</p>\n<p>We use <a href=\"https://drone.io/\">Drone</a> for our Automated deployments. </p>\n<p>Once you signed up for Kudoo cloud through the <a href=\"https://portal.kudoo.io\">Portal</a> all you need to do to activate your Drone account is to visit <a href=\"https://drone.kudoo.io\">https://drone.kudoo.io</a> and then authorise the application.\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.25%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Authorise Drone\"\n        title=\"Authorise Drone\"\n        src=\"/static/720462b55e1b7e6fe35945909da33ade/799d3/drone-authorisation.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/720462b55e1b7e6fe35945909da33ade/00d96/drone-authorisation.png 148w,\n/static/720462b55e1b7e6fe35945909da33ade/0b23c/drone-authorisation.png 295w,\n/static/720462b55e1b7e6fe35945909da33ade/799d3/drone-authorisation.png 590w,\n/static/720462b55e1b7e6fe35945909da33ade/2a3d6/drone-authorisation.png 885w,\n/static/720462b55e1b7e6fe35945909da33ade/ae92f/drone-authorisation.png 1180w,\n/static/720462b55e1b7e6fe35945909da33ade/eff2e/drone-authorisation.png 1920w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\nYou will now have access to Drone.</p>\n<p>You can now open the <code class=\"language-text\">web-app</code> repository\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/ec5555b59543c16a9c400f2cb12df1e2/26890/drone-repo.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 47.05357142857143%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Web app repository\"\n        title=\"Web app repository\"\n        src=\"/static/ec5555b59543c16a9c400f2cb12df1e2/799d3/drone-repo.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/ec5555b59543c16a9c400f2cb12df1e2/00d96/drone-repo.png 148w,\n/static/ec5555b59543c16a9c400f2cb12df1e2/0b23c/drone-repo.png 295w,\n/static/ec5555b59543c16a9c400f2cb12df1e2/799d3/drone-repo.png 590w,\n/static/ec5555b59543c16a9c400f2cb12df1e2/2a3d6/drone-repo.png 885w,\n/static/ec5555b59543c16a9c400f2cb12df1e2/26890/drone-repo.png 1120w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Under the source directory there will be a file called <code class=\"language-text\">.drone.yml</code>. </p>\n<h3>Configuring your Pipelines</h3>\n<p>In order for your deployments to work you’ll need to enter the <code class=\"language-text\">secrets</code> of your application.</p>\n<p>NODE<em>ENV=development\nGRAPHQL</em>API<em>URL=<a href=\"http://localhost:4000/api/\">http://localhost:4000/api/</a>\nSKELM</em>BASE_URL=<a href=\"http://localhost:4000\">http://localhost:4000</a></p>\n<h2>Manual deployments</h2>\n<p>To do this you’ll need to clone you app your app locally.</p>\n<p>You’ll need to make sure you have <a href=\"https://nodejs.org/en/download/\">Node installed</a></p>\n<p>Then make sure you are using the correct version. As of this writing, the latest LTS version of Node is version 12. </p>\n<p><strong>Please note</strong> Kudoo will always use the currently active LTS node release.</p>\n<p>Now make sure you have <a href=\"https://github.com/firebase/firebase-tools\">Firebase Tools</a> installed by running:\n<code class=\"language-text\">npm install -g firebase-tools</code></p>\n<p>You can now run\n<code class=\"language-text\">firebase deploy</code>\nto deploy your app.</p>","frontmatter":{"title":""}},"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"id":"37de802e-00c6-5bfc-b18a-b35fd8500e2c","frontmatter":{"title":""},"fields":{"slug":"/developer/v1/datamodel/"}}},{"node":{"id":"47f8b669-e3bd-59f0-a087-45dc5bb8a78f","frontmatter":{"title":""},"fields":{"slug":"/developer/v1/documents/"}}},{"node":{"id":"65a869a4-1e72-534e-99a7-fc79329a60ca","frontmatter":{"title":""},"fields":{"slug":"/developer/v1/"}}},{"node":{"id":"ed893806-6e35-5d77-bcfe-eb647c2c40cd","frontmatter":{"title":""},"fields":{"slug":"/developer/v1/menu-screens/"}}},{"node":{"id":"fb56de1b-76ca-58b9-9b01-f152e3adb33f","frontmatter":{"title":""},"fields":{"slug":"/developer/v1/pubsub/"}}},{"node":{"id":"a5bb2984-6af1-5e60-a8ef-2b2158027038","frontmatter":{"title":""},"fields":{"slug":"/developer/v1/screens/"}}},{"node":{"id":"fe539be1-9ca9-5518-a6b6-233fc97f1802","frontmatter":{"title":""},"fields":{"slug":"/governance/current/community/"}}},{"node":{"id":"9114754e-27cf-525c-813c-6f7be817a7a3","frontmatter":{"title":""},"fields":{"slug":"/governance/current/governance/"}}},{"node":{"id":"36e78aa4-a934-5030-8e9